      <title>墨西哥经济放缓幅度略高于预期，因利率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/mexico-s-economy-slows-slightly-more-than-expected-as-rates-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于近两年的两位数借贷成本对需求造成压力，墨西哥第二季度经济增速较前三个月有所放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/mexico-s-economy-slows-slightly-more-than-expected-as-rates-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:13:36 GMT</pubDate>
